 1160.1, 1069.9, 1181.0]}, {"text": "information they need to efficiently research, plan, book and experience travel. We have created a global travel", "bbox": [143.7, 1185.2, 1093.2, 1206.0]}, {"text": "marketplace used by a broad range of leisure and corporate travelers and offline retail travel agents. We make", "bbox": [143.7, 1210.1, 1083.0, 1230.9]}, {"text": "available, on a stand-alone and package basis, travel products and services provided by numerous airlines,", "bbox": [143.7, 1235.1, 1049.8, 1256.0]}, {"text": "lodging properties, car rental companies, destination service providers, cruise lines and other travel product", "bbox": [143.7, 1260.2, 1059.3, 1281.0]}, {"text": "and service companies. For additional information about our portfolio of brands, see the disclosure set forth in", "bbox": [143.7, 1285.1, 1088.1, 1305.9]}, {"text": "Part I, Item 1, Business, under the caption “Management Overview.”", "bbox": [143.7, 1310.1, 729.3, 1331.0]}, {"text": "Trends", "bbox": [164.6, 1371.7, 224.3, 1392.5]}, {"text": "The travel industry, which includes travel agencies and travel suppliers has been characterized by rapid", "bbox": [185.4, 1415.4, 1066.4, 1436.2]}, {"text": "and significant change. The U.S. airline sector has experienced significant turmoil in recent years, with several", "bbox": [143.7, 1440.3, 1090.2, 1461.1]}, {"text": "of the largest airlines seeking the protection of Chapter 11 bankruptcy proceedings.", "bbox": [143.7, 1465.3, 855.6, 1486.2]}, {"text": "29", "bbox": [608.4, 1515.3, 629.2, 1536.1]}]}